  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Fall of Mistwood</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">Landing of the Golden Company</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Mistwood\" title=\"Mistwood\">Mistwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nGolden Company victory<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne1_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/30px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/45px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/60px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:</b><br />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Mertyns.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Mertyns.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/20px-House_Mertyns.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/30px-House_Mertyns.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/40px-House_Mertyns.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mertyns\" title=\"House Mertyns\">House Mertyns</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>:</b><br />\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Golden_Company.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/30px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/45px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/60px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Mertyns.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Mertyns.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/20px-House_Mertyns.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/30px-House_Mertyns.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e2/House_Mertyns.svg/40px-House_Mertyns.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Mary_Mertyns\" title=\"Mary Mertyns\">Mary Mertyns</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:Golden_Company.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/20px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/30px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/40px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Young_John_Mudd\" title=\"Young John Mudd\">Young John Mudd</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:Golden_Company.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/20px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/30px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/40px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Chains\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chains\">Chains</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Mertyns garrison</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      More than 23 men</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>fall of Mistwood</b> occurs amidst the <a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">Landing of the Golden Company</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Mistwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In his campaign to place <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> joins the <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> in invading the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. Their <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> fleet is scattered by a storm after <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, and only six of the sellswords' ten ships arrive at the rendezvous near the <a href=\"/index.php/Rainwood\" title=\"Rainwood\">rainwood</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Cape_Wrath\" title=\"Cape Wrath\">Cape Wrath</a>, land formerly owned by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">House Connington</a>. The gathered force is not quite half the Golden Company's full strength of ten thousand.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Mistwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During her journey to meet Aegon, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> learns that Mistwood has fallen to the Golden Company.<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne1_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Half a mile from Mistwood, her party is ambushed by three Company men who escort them to the castle. There she meets with <a href=\"/index.php/Young_John_Mudd\" title=\"Young John Mudd\">Young John Mudd</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Chains\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chains\">Chains</a> who held the castle for the Company. She later has supper in the Tower of Owls with them and the dowager Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Mary_Mertyns\" title=\"Mary Mertyns\">Mary Mertyns</a> and her <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> who have been made prisoners in their own castle. Lady Mary explains to Arianne that the castle fell easily as the castle was lightly garrisoned since her sons and grandsons took most of the men to war in support of King <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>. Arianne and her companions leave for <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a> in the morning.<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne2_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne2-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Mistwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-arianne1-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne1_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne1_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 61\">Chapter 61</a>, The Griffin Reborn.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-arianne2-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne2_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Template:War of the Five Kings\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Template talk:War of the Five Kings\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:War_of_the_Five_Kings&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">Theaters and Campaigns of the War of the Five Kings</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" sty